          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1678294423059-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped leek</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
